Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:03.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watching Fairy Tail keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on an S class quest, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:19.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to Galuna Island without permission from the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:25.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray and Erza got involved, and although we managed to handle Lyon's plan to resurrect Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:29.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please destroy the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:41.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:52.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:10.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:15.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:23.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:29.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:40.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:51.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:12.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to destroy that moon right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll destroy the moon, and everyone will return to their original forms!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we get to see the moon destroyed right before our eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finally be back to our old selves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna destroy the moon, wouldn't being on top of the ruins help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's higher up than here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the villagers can't get near the ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is Erza we're talking about, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:44.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What does she plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite heart-racing, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In a lot of ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Giant Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It powers up my ability to throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lance of Haja, which repels the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll chuck that at the moon and blow it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that's not gonna work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However I do not think it will reach the moon with only this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to give me a boost with your flame's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:28.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I throw the spear, hit the back-end of the lance as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:35.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By combining the throwing power of the Giant Armor and your flames, we will destroy that moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:41.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the two of them so into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:44.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not {\i1}actually{\i0} going to destroy the moon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach it! To that Sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're destroyin' stuff again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the moon that she broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This island was covered by an evil lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lens?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A gas was released during the creation of the moon drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That gas crystallized and became a lens covering the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to the lens that the moon looked purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the evil lens broken, this island's true radiance should return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:36.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:40.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not... going back to normal? {This was Gray's line}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Everything is the way it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil lens didn't affect their bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it affected their memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The false memory that they became demons during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They were demons from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Now that you mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a bit confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They all have the power to change into humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They ended up thinking that their human forms were who they really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the false memory that the moon drip caused in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why were Lyon and the others okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they are human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:39.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it only affects the memories of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:45.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also because they are demons that they can't get near those ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:50.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beings of darkness could never get near ruins that have absorbed so much holy light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I trusted this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wizards... Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dude from the boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:16.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't die from being stabbed in the chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You disappeared from the boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't tell you the truth back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:29.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one who gained back my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I left this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since all the people of the village thought they were humans, they were all scared of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally back to normal, huh, pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobo's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Demon Island, indeed... {This is a reference to earlier when Galuna was first discussed. They called it the Demon Isle in the manga. I don't recall your wording in the anime though...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know... Just looking at all their faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They look less like devils...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and more like angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:29.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight we're having a feast! A demon's feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet a demon's feast is gonna get kind of rowdy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:33.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your injuries feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recognize me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you came to this village, we think you're just the greatest, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you like us better in our human forms, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this look kind of works for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray's so kind, I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're full of confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dance together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do the groovy demon's dance! {This translation of groovy is stolen from the localization of Eyetoy: Furifuri Dance Tengoku from "Eyetoy: Groove" for the sony playstation2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Gray's popular with {\i1}those{\i0} kind of girls, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he's having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as he says...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all feel that our appearance is a weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so we never interacted with any other islands...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we started the rumor that Galuna Island was cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:04.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the people at the port were scared of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on, I think we'll be able to get along better with the people from the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should cooperate and help each other. {This part wasn't in the manga, so if they come in like the eagles, it'll have to be in a filler episode}{Why do I see a scene out of "The Hobbit" occuring in about ~5 volumes where a flock of demons flies in to save the day?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you speak to them in this way, it won't matter how you look, you'll be understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:38.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We can't be satisfied like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:40.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here with Reitei Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:10.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:13.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Reitei's pals?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them to us. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys did Reitei Lyon pretty good... He can't even move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have come to pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:42.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Didn't you hear? We and Lyon have already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:43.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a separate issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will end this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Show me what you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't keep relying on you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect our own village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can appreciate the sentiment. However leave this matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's Titania?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did me quite a service on that beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Erza! That woman can manipulate rocks and trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And weird eyebrows dude can neutralize magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:32.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I better finish this up before they can pull any tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's strong barehanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such is the Great Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:47.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Great?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true... We're no match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this doesn't atone for our actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we wanted to finish things off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what they meant by "pay back."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard from Reitei-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:20.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we're free of our hatred for Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you guys also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our towns were destroyed when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends and family burned to ashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:36.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reitei-sama was finally going to defeat Deliora. That's why we followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:43.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's still no reason to hurt innocent people in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We hated Deliora so much, we ended up becoming no better than it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here and eat with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were your enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:06.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I eat things with a lot of calories, my weight will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's live it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you return the village to the way it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it a bonus. {That might work with otaku who know the Japanese use of the word, but not for a more general audience. How about, "Call it a bonus."}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to do with you?  But Fairy Tail exceeded my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they never get in our way. {But of course they do. Doesn't Siegrain realize that he's in a shonen adventure manga?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd 'brows and the chick go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After they couldn't eat any more, they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you'll be left with a scar. {She's talking about the one scar on his forehead}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It doesn't bother me. {You used "don't care" below}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:18.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care where I get scarred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a wound you can't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I say somethin' cool, don't step all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:30.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't take the reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Your gratitude is all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was not a job our guild officially accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few idiots running off to do a job on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, that doesn't change the fact that you saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I say this is not a reward for the guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:05.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a "thanks" to our friends for saving us, would you accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say no when you put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,70 million jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However taking it would be against the guild's principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:25.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be happy to take only the key you offered as the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:31.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy to take you back to Hargeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I have a ship ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You hijacked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Madame?" {this subitle progam makes similar consecutive titles look like the same title, so by adding the quotation marks, I hope to differentiate between the pirate's line and Lucy's}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have taken a liking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such is the Great Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with "the Great" already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you mates come on board as well! {this isn't a literal translation, but similar.  "Shatei" implies he thinks of the rest of the gang as Erza's lackeys or younger accomplises in crime.  I'm sort of replacing it with a more common pirate terminology for the same thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:16:59.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:02.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww! I don't want to board that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy to swim instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back and dance with us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come see us anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There they go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:44.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:51.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this? And after finally reuniting with your younger fellow pupil...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words... love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Are guilds any fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame about Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, too bad, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it would have already been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I'd be one step closer to my dream if I got my hands on Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Siegrain-sama. I didn't expect that woman's magic to be so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be talking about her that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul's tears... Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If she had lived, she would have surely become one of the 10 Wizard Saints. {This is one of the approved names}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:55.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was a miserable woman so obsessed with magic that my father abandoned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:19:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you lose, the more power you can obtain. {Referring to either Ultear losing Ul or Ul losing Ultear--either way, the only one who gave up anything was Ultear's father}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was of little consequence to my mother. {"Just a little thing" sounds like her height when she was small}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising those two students was her lingering affection for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us proceed to the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong with your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It swells up now? {I learned "hareru" after I threw out my knee a couple of years ago}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what are your impressions fighting Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:34.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even use half of my power, but it was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's gonna get stronger and stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The son of Igneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs to keep burning bright, for my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:59.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But man... All that work, and one key is all we get?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was a full-blown S class quest, too. {Officially S class should also have the hyphen since "S" modifies "class" and not "quest" but I'm treating S class quest as an entire unit}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This much is just about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:08.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup! No complaints!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one it's of any use to, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You thieving cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:21.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there are only 12 of the gold "Zodiac" keys in the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're super-duper rare, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That cow and maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:30.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I progress, my Spirits will get way stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:34.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the key we got this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Archer, Sagittarius! {I wouldn't have gone that non-literal, but it's your call}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that half man, half horse?! {considering the non-literal translation of "jinba", I'm implying that Gray knows sagittarius is a half man half horse thing here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think it's the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a man or a horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:45.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Easygoing, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten that you'll be punished when we get back, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:51.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd dropped that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:21:01.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Accepting your actions was a field decision on my part. {indicating that it was her decision and not a guild decision}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still must receive your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:12.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should be mostly forgiven for what happened this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However your judge will be the master. {playing a little with "defending" in the next line}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:17.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have no intention of defending you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So be prepared to take your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna make us do {\i1}that{\i0}, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:26.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! I never want to do {\i1}that{\i0} again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it. We did a good job, so gramps'll be impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How frightfully positive of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:38.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think it's pretty much decided already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it. {Ude ga naru is a phrase meaning <-- that}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that! Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:49.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:52.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, what the heck is {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:55.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:02.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:05.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:15.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:32.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:45.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:56.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:23:05.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:09.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:16.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:29.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:34.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Happy's Fairy Tail Lectures!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:38.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're going introduce a lot of other Fairy Tail members!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.05,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild consists of wizards who Master Makarov gathered! They can use all kinds of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:42.25,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.25,0:23:43.75,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.25,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:46.79,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirajane
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:50.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although everyone is always fighting, in truth we all get along great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:54.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, Bow, Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure would be handy to be able to fly like you, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! But that'd be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, unless you and me completely switched magics.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:10.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I wonder if anyone dropped magic like that around somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu. You can't drop magic.
